    <div class="row">
      <h2>我们带你认识</h2>
      <h4>来自世界各地的朋友</h4>
      <div class="col-sm-4 ">
        <div class="thumbnail">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-globe logo"></span>
          <div class="caption">
