          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 ">
        <div class="thumbnail">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-gift logo"></span>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>人生好时节</h3>
            <p>成长和收获是最好的礼物</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4 ">
        <div class="thumbnail">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-book logo"></span>
          <div class="caption">
